  "strategy": [
    "Prioritize marker_seen: immediately switch to marker_track and approach.",
    "On marker_lost during tracking/approach, switch to scan_full to reacquire.",
    "On marker_close, always transition to goal_stop (terminal state with only stop enabled).",
    "After obstacle detection, recover via rotation or scan, then return to exploration.",
    "In clear, alternate between forward progress and scan actions to maximize marker detection.",
    "Enable only one controllable per state (except obs_front, which allows both rotate and scan for robust escape).",
    "Helper commit states ensure one-shot action execution before returning to decision/perception.",
    "All uncontrollable events are handled in every state (total w.r.t. uncontrollables).",
    "No oscillatory or ambiguous transitions; recovery and search are deterministic.",
    "No direct move_forward from obs_front; always pass through a recovery/scan state."
  ]
